<title>BRAZIL: RESEARCH ALERT - Lightpar downgraded to hold.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Lightpar downgraded to hold.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Deutsche Morgan Grenfell said in a report it downgraded Brazil's Light Participacoes (Lightpar) to hold from buy.</p>
<p>-- It said the stock has risen 64 percent in the last three months, outperforming the Ibovespa index by 24 percent.</p>
<p>-- Lightpar's current price is now only eight percent below their year-end target price of $330.</p>
<p>-- Lightpar's common shares were off 0.32 percent at 314 reais ($298.8).</p>
<p>((-- Romina Nicaretta, Sao Paulo newsroom, 5511 248 5415))</p>
